synthesis: This ties into broader market movement and sentiment.

timeline.text: The Labour Codes have ignited significant tension, leading unions to prepare for a strong display of opposition on November 26. This confrontation reflects a deeper struggle within the labor market, as workers advocate for their rights amid evolving regulations.
